### 1. 회원가입
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/signup/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@elaw.kr",
  "password": "test1234!",
  "name": "테스트유저",
  "role": "student"
}

###

### 2. 로그인 (JWT 토큰 발급)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@elaw.kr",
  "password": "test1234!"
}

###

### 3. 백준 아이디 등록
